# the team is structured (single operator) while still recording the
# commitment that no path is unowned.
#
# Format documented at:
#   https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# When the team grows, this file gets domain-specific entries (e.g.
# infra/postgres-related paths owned by an SRE; legal/* owned by counsel
# once retained). Until then, the wildcard captures the reality.

